{"tid":1482214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"TG單身谷招人","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T14:18:03.000Z","uid":242422,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b07c840874bebf49af7d15fcc80c49a386cb334","tid":1482214,"uid":242422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"TG單身谷<br />\n我地每個月最少搞一次活動,怕悶既你..<br />\n一齊黎吹水啦..我地最多係單身既靚仔靚女!<br />\n想識另一半既你仲唔填下面張Form加入我地? 只限24-35歲<br />\n男女比例維持平衡 !   男女比例維持平衡!   男女比例維持平衡!   好重要要講3次<br />\n大家請耐心等候~~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd0FxnS8VgnXJrZoXPba4-zCUYwTh8a0kXRBaMOylLjhvsoig/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd0FxnS8VgnXJrZoXPba4-zCUYwTh8a0kXRBaMOylLjhvsoig%2Fviewform&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=9e3603ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd0FxnS8VgnXJrZoXPba4-zCUYwTh8a0kXRBaMOylLjhvsoig/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"a74b09db9deedf71c2189ed262bec2639bd71548","tid":1482214,"uid":139409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=e925e673\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=e925e673\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"9067019975603711db4941def19110d7d67bda24","tid":1482214,"uid":242422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf61dd06d971c03ce35236cfc36dd579f91c5d6","tid":1482214,"uid":242422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633c2a2